# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Internal-only: only the CORE APPLICATION (html/js/css + backend/) ships
# publicly. Everything that is a log, plan, learning/reference/decision doc, or
# dev/test scaffolding stays local. (Decided 2026-07-04.)
# (.gitignore has no inline comments — patterns must be alone on their line.)
#   LAUNCH.md        = launch plan (security gaps + strategy)
#   CHRONICLE.md     = build-story log w/ internal decisions
#   CONTEXT.md       = domain glossary (reference doc)
#   docs/            = ADRs (decision records) + architecture learning docs
#   tutor-poc.html   = tutor stage-0 POC (dev scaffolding)
#   test-sections.txt= internal test data
#   prototypes/      = theme/design exploration mockups
LAUNCH.md
CHRONICLE.md
CONTEXT.md
docs/
tutor-poc.html
test-sections.txt
prototypes/
